11:T4c5,In the film "When Evil Lurks," I approached it with reservations, unsure of what to expect. The entire movie is presented in Spanish with subtitles, allowing me to follow the storyline. It unfolds as a Spanish take on the exorcism theme, reminiscent of "The Exorcist." However, instead of an exorcism, the focus is on Satan possessing bodies, moving from one to another after each host's death, always transferring to the person responsible for the previous death.

The film's execution left much to be desired, lacking a coherent script and veering off in multiple directions. The actors did their best with the material provided, but the disjointed narrative made it challenging to anticipate the next plot development.

A concerning moment arises when a child appears on screen completely naked, a gratuitous and unnecessary inclusion that crosses a line. Such a scene is unwarranted and inappropriate, detracting from the viewing experience and raising ethical concerns.

Overall, "When Evil Lurks" fails to deliver a compelling and cohesive story, marred by questionable choices and a lack of narrative clarity. This misstep, especially involving a child actor, overshadows any potential the film may have had.5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Movie\",\"name\":\"When Evil Lurks\",\"description\":\"Residents of a small rural town discover that a demon is about to be born among them. They desperately try to escape before the evil is born, but it may be too late.\",\"image\":\"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iQ7G9LhP7NRRIUM4Vlai3eOxBAc.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2023-10-05\",\"numberOfEpisodes\":null,\"countryOfOrigin\":\"AR\",\"inLanguage\":\"es\",\"genre\":[\"Horror\",\"Thriller\",null,null,null],\"aggregateRating\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateRating\",\"ratingValue\":7.163,\"bestRating\":10,\"ratingCount\":1384}}"}}],["$","$L10",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"fc17b7e4-fff8-4441-bef6-28301dfed0ad","tmdb_id":744857,"imdb_id":"tt16300962","content_type":"movie","title":"When Evil Lurks","original_title":"Cuando acecha la maldad","overview":"Residents of a small rural town discover that a demon is about to be born among them. They desperately try to escape before the evil is born, but it may be too late.","poster_path":"/iQ7G9LhP7NRRIUM4Vlai3eOxBAc.jpg","backdrop_path":"/cavK9ox37pxDg11RvJINMH63onU.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-05","first_air_date":null,"status":"published","original_language":"es","origin_country":["AR","US"],"genres":[{"id":27,"name":"Horror"},{"id":53,"name":"Thriller"},"psychological horror","horror film","psychological horror fiction"],"popularity":3.4587,"vote_average":7.163,"vote_count":1384,"runtime":100,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":null,"created_at":"2026-02-26T01:34:22.838996+00:00","updated_at":"2026-02-26T01:34:22.607+00:00","tagline":"There's no point in praying.","homepage":null,"budget":0,"revenue":209