cond HBO special, diving into a wide range of topics including why she doesn't want kids, the harsh realities of aging, her sexual fantasies and more.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4159,"vote_count":32,"poster_path":"/ekEtVXAuWPwLz6Afv4m7KjORGCe.jpg","release_date":"2024-05-10","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/odaJLtRx1lIdK00BZ81SmdrmAom.jpg","original_title":"Nikki Glaser: Someday You'll Die","original_language":"en"},{"id":910858,"adult":false,"title":"The Estate","video":false,"overview":"Down-on-her-luck divorcee Macey and her fickle sister Savanna attempt to win over their terminally ill, difficult-to-please Aunt Hilda in hopes of becoming the beneficiaries of her wealthy estate, only to find the rest of their greedy family members have the same idea.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7953,"vote_count":124,"poster_path":"/mYgS4djsVj61kzEpX43LklGUfgK.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-04","vote_average":5.375,"backdrop_path":"/2Lx15Nv0fCmbsPJeJ8RAzIWxRda.jpg","original_title":"The Estate","original_language":"en"},{"id":1032372,"adult":false,"title":"Cold Meat","video":false,"overview":"David Petersen is passing through the Colorado Rockies. After saving a young diner waitress from her violent ex-husband during a break from driving, he hits the road again alone through a dangerous snow blizzard. One false move behind the wheel has him waking up inside a ravine, in the eye of the storm. But the cold is the least of his worries when a beast starts prowling outside. How will he survive?","genre_ids":[53,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8001,"vote_count":138,"poster_path":"/gcACvRRy9nE9de5gTetoXiheIZ5.jpg","release_date":"2024-02-23","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/h1An6CRfuzwlUAKtnmGpKuHCW37.jpg","original_title":"Cold Meat","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":861303,"adult":false,"title":"Glitche","video":false,"overview":"Glitche is experiencing programming errors. Please avoid all drug.exe.