ock Saints","video":false,"overview":"Tired of the crime overrunning the streets of Boston, Irish Catholic twin brothers Conner and Murphy are inspired by their faith to cleanse their hometown of evil with their own brand of zealous vigilante justice. As they hunt down and kill one notorious gangster after another, they become controversial folk heroes in the community. But Paul Smecker, an eccentric FBI agent, is fast closing in on their blood-soaked trail.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":4.189,"vote_count":2615,"poster_path":"/wtLUmkWg41xFLpvmUWAN1mm65f6.jpg","release_date":"1999-01-22","vote_average":7.252,"backdrop_path":"/9DNDELpVxuLJWMoomgULhhZFoHR.jpg","original_title":"The Boondock Saints","original_language":"en"},{"id":8382,"adult":false,"title":"Today You Die","video":false,"overview":"A former thief who is trying to go straight seeks vengeance on those who framed him.","genre_ids":[28,80,12,53],"popularity":1.6619,"vote_count":121,"poster_path":"/fSL56vXRp4Qh23vXPiAhJMFKZgB.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-13","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":"/9XpbzvX38LUi21QYvBlVyp3yBMv.jpg","original_title":"Today You Die","original_language":"en"},{"id":8398,"adult":false,"title":"The Hitcher","video":false,"overview":"While driving through the New Mexico Desert during a rainy night, college students Jim Halsey and his girlfriend Grace Andrews give a ride to a hitchhiker. While in their car, the stranger proves to be a psychopath threatening the young couple with a knife, but Jim successfully throws him out of the car. This sets off a chain of events that will change all of their lives forever.","genre_ids":[80,27,53],"popularity":1.5666,"vote_count":969,"poster_path":"/b3As3DylhyrL8xeGptElGnkfb42.jpg","release_date":"2007-01-19","vote_average":5.874,"backdrop_path":"/2w0uvzOXKyda8fW0IvkdGFFnJCq.jpg","original_title":"The Hitcher","original_language":"en"},{"id":8413,"adult":false,"title":"Event Horizon","video":false,"overview":"In 2047, a group of astronauts are