ter with mysterious lights that appear over her small town. She soon develops dangerous, supernatural abilities, and turns to her childhood friend Sean. The authorities target them and a chase ensues as officials try to discover the truth behind Alex's transformation.","genre_ids":[53,878],"popularity":1.2167,"vote_count":143,"poster_path":"/wez4hCV7ltekZwRkQVyiKEZNrm5.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-05","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/rexivjdRPxvcqMFU1cHY3g1IaZa.jpg","original_title":"At First Light","original_language":"en"},{"id":8843,"adult":false,"title":"The Cell","video":false,"overview":"A psychotherapist journeys inside a comatose serial killer in the hopes of saving his latest victim.","genre_ids":[27,878,53],"popularity":3.6702,"vote_count":1669,"poster_path":"/kfYVxvDDAJoFq2knHUzAZP09pAc.jpg","release_date":"2000-08-18","vote_average":6.267,"backdrop_path":"/wMvqec4N7Na5DHdyQugh7w0UpBF.jpg","original_title":"The Cell","original_language":"en"},{"id":8987,"adult":false,"title":"The River Wild","video":false,"overview":"Gail and Tom Hartman are struggling to stay together and decide to take a white-water rafting holiday adventure in Montana for their son Roarke's 10th birthday, only to meet up with a pair of mysterious men whose desperation grows, turning their vacation into a nightmare.","genre_ids":[12,53,18],"popularity":2.3322,"vote_count":939,"poster_path":"/wVgQ2T63ThjIsY4R0qoHXjyllql.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-30","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/yIWtX0ulnAUrbd12F9foRzHaT1M.jpg","original_title":"The River Wild","original_language":"en"},{"id":8991,"adult":false,"title":"Undead","video":false,"overview":"A quaint Australian fishing village is overcome by meteorites that turn its residents into the ravenous undead, leaving a small group of those unharmed to find a way out.","genre_ids":[27,28,35,878],"popularity":2.0908,"vote_count":235,"poster_path":"/jwXrKFO20FTvA7mHqnTvMXSznDS.jpg","release_date":"2003-09-04","vote_average":5.46,"backdrop_path":"/rWwcX62LLBiIuVOP8bxMAWbIdTB.jpg","original_title":"Undead","original_language":"en"},{"id":8995,"adult":false,"title":"C(r)ook","video":false,"overview":"A killer for the Russian Mafia in Vienna wants to retire and write a book about his passion - cooking. The mafia godfather suspects treason.","genre_ids":[35,80,53],"popularity":0.3672,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/ebH7UcxveEudlhzlmfRBu2Tneq.jpg","release_date":"2004-11-11","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/8i4GUCNk8MDCjFMQ5e6SgHb3sLP.jpg","original_title":"c[r]ook","original_language":"de"},{"id":8851,"adult":false,"title":"The Blob","video":false,"overview":"A drive-in favorite, this sci-fi classic follows teenagers Steve and his best girl, Jane, as they try to protect their hometown from a gelatinous alien life form that engulfs everything it touches. The first to discover the substance and live to tell about it, Steve and Jane witness the blob destroying an elderly man, then it growing to a terrifying size. But no one else has seen the goo, and policeman Dave refuses to believe the kids without proof.","genre_ids":[27,878],"popularity":1.9879,"vote_count":646,"poster_path":"/ctOwn1Ibg3SjDG4WulvFvSH0PRT.jpg","release_date":"1958-09-10","vote_average":6.215,"backdrop_path":"/32l2szM3oY7kdI3TMBral5dsc2E.jpg","original_title":"The Blob","original_language":"en"},{"id":8852,"adult":false,"title":"Prince of Darkness","video":false,"overview":"A priest discovers an ancient canister containing a strange liquid in an abandoned church. When a group of graduate students and scientists are tasked with studying it, they unknowingly unleash an evil force waiting to destroy all of humanity.","genre_ids":[27],"popularity":1.6304,"vote_count":1118,"poster_path":"/jjcAOhtGuX4p8XvlVn1WXUT1jWi.jpg","release_date":"1987-10-23","vote_average":6.779,"backdrop_path":"/9FYa8R1VQdgfuX4QcgZgvbaQ2ca.jpg","original_title":"Prince of Darkness","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt16300962","twitter_id":null,"